      <title>美联储鲍曼表示目前还不适合降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-25/fed-s-bowman-says-not-yet-appropriate-to-cut-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事米歇尔鲍曼周二在伦敦发表讲话时表示，“我们尚未达到降低政策利率的适当程度”，并警告通胀存在上行风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-25/fed-s-bowman-says-not-yet-appropriate-to-cut-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 12:09:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
